official_title: A bill to name the Federal Building in Omaha, Nebraska, the "Glenn Cunningham Federal Building" in commemoration of the many contributions of former Congressman Glenn Cunningham.

summary.text: Provides for the naming of the Federal Building in Omaha, Nebraska, as the "Glenn Cunningham Federal Building" in commemoration of the many contributions of former Congressman Glenn Cunningham.
